# Manda App — Architecture Decision Record

**Version:** 1.0 — MVP
**Status:** In development
**Audience:** Engineers, Tech Leads, AI agents working on `manda-app/`

> **Scope:** Stack, routing model, auth lifecycle, API client, theming, and conventions for the Manda mobile/web client. Relevant whenever working under `app/**`, `providers/**`, `lib/**`, `components/**`, `hooks/**`, `constants/**`, `app.json`, or `tsconfig.json`.

---

## 1. Context and Goals

Manda App is the mobile client (iOS / Android / web via `react-native-web`) for the Manda conversational exchange platform. It consumes the `api` REST service and connects to `ws-gateway` over WebSocket for realtime messaging.

| Concern              | Decision                                                |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| Targets              | iOS, Android, web (Expo Go-compatible during MVP)       |
| Distribution         | Expo SDK 54 with New Architecture enabled               |
| Backend coupling     | REST for everything except live messages, WS for stream |
| Offline strategy     | Deferred — MVP requires connectivity                    |

---

## 2. Architectural Decisions

| Decision         | Choice                                       | Rationale                                                                      |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Framework        | Expo SDK 54 · React Native 0.81 · React 19   | Single codebase for iOS/Android/web; `newArchEnabled` on for Fabric/TurboModules |
| Routing          | `expo-router` 6 with typed routes            | File-based routing; route groups isolate auth vs app shells                    |
| Server state     | TanStack Query v5                            | Built-in caching, retries, invalidation; pairs cleanly with REST               |
| HTTP             | Axios with interceptors                      | Request bearer injection + 401-triggered single-flight refresh                 |
| Secure storage   | `expo-secure-store`                          | Keychain/Keystore-backed token storage; **never AsyncStorage for tokens**      |
| Theming          | Custom `MANDA` palette + Navigation Theme    | Brand-first; legacy `Colors` retained for `themed-*` primitives                |
| Fonts            | `@expo-google-fonts/plus-jakarta-sans` (5wt) | Loaded once at root via `useFonts`                                             |
| Path alias       | `@/*` → project root                         | Avoids deep relatives; enforced by `tsconfig.json`                             |
| Package manager  | npm                                          | Project-local (the backend monorepo uses pnpm — don't mix)                     |
| React Compiler   | Enabled (`experiments.reactCompiler`)        | Don't pre-optimize with `useMemo`/`useCallback` unless profiling proves it     |

