## 7. TanStack Query Defaults (`lib/query-client.ts`)

```ts
queries: {
  staleTime: 30_000,
  refetchOnWindowFocus: false,
  retry: (n, err) =>
    !(err instanceof ApiError && err.status >= 400 && err.status < 500)
    && n < 2,
}
mutations: { retry: false }
```

Rule of thumb: **never retry 4xx** (auth failure, validation), retry transient (5xx / network) up to 2×, focus-driven refetches are off for mobile.

