## 8. Secure Storage (`lib/api/storage.ts`)

| Key                          | Contents              |
| ---------------------------- | --------------------- |
| `manda.auth.accessToken`     | JWT access (HS256)    |
| `manda.auth.refreshToken`    | Opaque refresh        |

API: `authStorage.load() / save({ accessToken, refreshToken }) / clear()`. `load()` returns `null` if **either** token is missing — partial state is treated as unauthenticated.

> **Hard rule:** tokens live in SecureStore only. Never AsyncStorage, MMKV, files, or component state.

