## 12. Mobile ↔ Backend Contract (quick reference)

| Concern        | Mobile                                                | Backend (`api` / `ws-gateway`)             |
| -------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| Auth header    | `Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>`                 | api validates HS256 + jti denylist         |
| Refresh        | `POST /auth/refresh { refreshToken }` (single-flight) | rotates + reuse-detects via `family_id`    |
| Logout         | `POST /auth/logout { refreshToken }` + SecureStore clear | revokes refresh family + access jti     |
| WebSocket auth | `Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: bearer.<accessToken>`        | ws-gateway validates via `@manda/shared`   |
| Heartbeat      | ping every 30s while connected                        | ws-gateway responds with pong              |
| Error payload  | parsed into `ApiError { message, status, body }`      | `{ statusCode, error, message, ... }` PT   |

