## 13. Deferred to Post-MVP

| Feature                            | Trigger to introduce                                       |
| ---------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |
| Offline message queue + outbox     | When users frequently lose connectivity mid-conversation   |
| Push notifications (APNs / FCM)    | After backend Notification service ships                   |
| Background sync                    | Once offline queue exists                                  |
| E2E tests (Maestro / Detox)        | After core flows stabilise                                 |
| EAS Build / OTA updates            | When moving off Expo Go for distribution                   |
| Localization (i18n) beyond PT      | When non-PT markets are targeted                           |
| Dark-mode-first redesign of MANDA  | When dark mode becomes a product priority                  |

